# Syncthing ignore patterns for ~/.claude-mem/
#
# Rename to `claude-mem.stignore` (strip .example) and deploy via install.sh
# (lands at ~/.claude-mem/.stignore).
#
# Semantics: see claude-config.stignore.example. Paths relative to folder root.

// ========================================================================
// DENY: SQLite transient files
// ========================================================================
// WAL / shared-memory files change constantly while DB is open.
// Syncthing replicating them mid-flight causes consistency issues.
// The DB file itself (.db) is safe to sync when no writer is active.
*.db-shm
*.db-wal
*.db-journal

// ========================================================================
// DENY: rotating logs (per-machine, not useful cross-machine)
// ========================================================================
/logs/

// ========================================================================
// ALLOWED (syncs):
//   /claude-mem.db         main SQLite (observations, sessions, prompts)
//   /chroma/               ChromaDB embeddings (vector index)
//   /settings.json         claude-mem config (stable)
//   /observer-sessions/    sessions em andamento (small)
// ========================================================================
